data.description: Rare opportunity to own a Luxury End Unit Condo in the Olympus Condominium. VA ASSUMABLE LOAN 2.25% Interest Rate. 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths - completely renovated. This unit comes with a parking space 3  X 7 X 7 in the secure parking garage.  Extra storage unit in garage area. All utilities and amenities are included in the monthly condo fee! Gym, event room, outside seating in park like setting.  Living room features floor to ceiling windows, & sliding door to a huge balcony with spectacular views! Bedrooms feature huge windows, Main Bedroom has private second balcony. Walk in closet has custom closet organizer Full size washer and dryer are in the unit. Great building management will provide you with excellent accommodations! Well maintained grounds and building - features new elevators, hallways, balconies, modern style foyer!Storage unit for Holiday decoration and or any extra items you don’t want in condo.  In addition to the pool, residents at Olympus enjoy a fitness center, tennis courts, party room, sauna and much more. Ideally located minutes to Van Dorn Metro station, close to I-395, The Pentagon, Crystal City, and downtown D.C. Amazing location. All utilities and amenities are included in the monthly condo fee. One inside  Garage Parking Spaces and one outside assigned parking space both very valuable. 4 EV charging stations in parking area.
